### When to Use FULL OUTER JOIN

- Find all unmatched records from both tables
- Data reconciliation and quality checks
- Finding orphaned records (employees without departments AND departments without employees)
- Complete data analysis

✅ **FULL OUTER JOIN is useful when you need to see the complete picture of data from both tables, including all unmatched records!**
